text: The Bahraini dinar (symbol: .de.parti or BD code: BHD 1965) is the currency of Bahrain. It was second strongest currencies in the world. It was listed in top 10 strongest currencies in the world. It was divided into 1000 fils. == References == == Other websites == * Banknotes of Bahrain Category:Bahrain Category:Currency of Asia
